<h5 id="subject_1114280">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;topic=125427.msg1114280#msg1114280" rel="nofollow">监察训诫 &amp; 监察者</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_1114280'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_1114280'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #1 于:</strong> 2021-05-23, 周日 21:52:20 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_1114280_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_1114280"><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">监察训诫（Monitor Obedience）</span></strong></span><br>出自 <a href="http://Source Concordance of Rivals pg. 3" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">Source Concordance of Rivals pg. 3</a><br><em>你每天的祈祷和对特定监察者半神的小型献祭会给你带来特别的增益。</em><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>先决条件：</strong></span>知识（位面）3级，必须信仰一位监察者半神<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">好处：</span></strong>每一名监察者半神都需要不同的训诫仪典，进行每一种仪典都仅需花费1小时。一旦你进行了训诫仪式，你就会根据该半神在仪典方法处所列出的内容而获得一项特殊能力或抵抗。<br>如果你至少有12生命骰，你在完成仪典后获得第一神恩。如果你至少有16生命骰，你在完成仪典后获得第二神恩。如果你至少有20生命骰，你在完成仪典后获得第三神恩。神恩效果都是持续性效果，除了那些特别写明持续时间或每日使用次数的。<br>一旦你无法进行每日仪典，你失去该专长获得的所有好处与神恩直到 你再一次进行仪典。<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>原文</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Monitor Obedience<br>Source Concordance of Rivals pg. 3<br>Your daily prayer and minor sacrifices to a particular monitor demigod grant you special boons.<br><br>Prerequisites: Knowledge (planes) 3 ranks, must worship a monitor demigod.<br><br>Benefit: Each monitor demigod requires a different obedience, but all obediences take only 1 hour to perform. Once you&#039;ve performed the obedience, you gain the benefit of a special ability or resistance as indicated in the Obedience entry for the demigod.<br><br>If you have at least 12 Hit Dice, you also gain the first boon granted by your monitor demigod upon undertaking your obedience. If you have at least 16 Hit Dice, you also gain the monitor demigod&#039;s second boon. If you have 20 Hit Dice or more, you also gain the monitor demigod&#039;s third boon. Unless a boon lists a specific duration or number of uses per day, its effects are constant.<br><br>If you ever fail to perform a daily obedience, you lose access to the benefits and boons granted by this feat until you next perform the obedience.</div></div></div><hr /><br>监察者<br>施工中</div>
</div>
</div>
